title: The Three world Taobao store
summary: Ning Xiaofan is a normal young man and his poor family is often bullied by rich and powerful classmates. Until one day, a magic software – “Taobao Sanjie Store” suddenly appeared on his cell phone. The life of the fans went a different way, and his counterattack began.
